<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Throughly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Throughly,</orth> thoroughly: <cit><quote>the next advantage will we take t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 3, 14</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>till thy wound be t. healed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.2.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 2, 115</bibl></cit>. <emph>if he had been t. moved,</emph> Wiv. <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">1, 4</bibl>, <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">1, 4</bibl> <cit><quote>we'll do it t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 5.260" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 260</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to quit me of them t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.202" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 202</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I am informed t. of the cause,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 173</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>now do your duty t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.4.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 4, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you scarce can right me t. then,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 99</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>most t. to be winnowed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.111" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 1, 111</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll be revenged most t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.136" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 136</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my point and period will be t. wrought,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 7, 97</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Lucius will do's commission t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 2.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 4, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I am t. weary,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.6.36" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 36</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>